<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Are you interested in languages and culture? Middle East/South Asia Studies is a unique major where you can learn about a region encompasses 44 countries. The major focuses on the Arab Gulf, Egypt, India, Iran, Israel, Lebanon, the Meghreb (North Africa), Palestine, Syria, and Turkey. Middle East/South Asia Studies majors also have the opportunity to get involved in research, special projects with faculty guidance, and study abroad.</p>
